with a bad drinking problem.

253
00:23:48,531 --> 00:23:51,576
Jody! Come on down for dinner!

254
00:23:53,036 --> 00:23:56,998
<i>I'm not hungry.</i>
You come down right now.

255
00:23:58,416 --> 00:24:00,919
