There are no heroes!

368
00:33:13,846 --> 00:33:17,391
<i>Only crazy men who lose their mind
in the middle of a battle.</i>

369
00:33:17,475 --> 00:33:21,312
<i>Every sane person's got his head down,
trying to stay alive.</i>

370
00:33:21,395 --> 00:33:23,731
But one lunatic...

371
00:33:23,814 --> 00:33:27,443
